{"tid":461072,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺街撞到自稱美斯嘅人","createTime":"2017-11-07T08:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T09:08:10.000Z","uid":53023,"like":12,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83373df353ec031a01a1d1df09ad2d5469d7f51d","tid":461072,"uid":53023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"話說小弟啱啱喺旺角行街，去到西洋菜南街一個轉個位嗰陣唔小心同一個男人相撞，我仲撞到佢副眼鏡跌咗落地。跟住係我地嘅對答：<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：喂，你撞到我喎<br />\n男人：（痞低執翻佢副眼鏡）<br />\n我：喂<br />\n男人：你都撞到我啦<br />\n<br />\n我聽得出佢係普通話口音，但我唔太聽得明佢講乜<br />\n利申：小學普通話唔合格<br />\n<br />\n我：你有無事啊？如果你都無事就打和啦，嘅然我地相撞<br />\n男人：我美斯啊 什麼打禾？你想要打架嗎？操<br />\n我：美斯？你係美斯咁我咪大J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人：為什麼我美斯你就是大雞巴？我操你媽B 想要幹架嗎 <br />\n<br />\n跟住我見到佢拎起電話好似想吹雞咁 我就跑走咗<br />\n<br />\n屌 估唔到美斯真人咁惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果下次見到佢應該點算？"},{"pid":"c20c6883b0b6338c98a38bd98ecec35b39e922ad","tid":461072,"uid":23039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"無是咁的 0分重作"},{"pid":"797a1117ee37644bd53d1d1084d64c2fc3be5b9a","tid":461072,"uid":58445,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"勉強冇幸福"},{"pid":"17c915292cfff1f853da4a8879eef96b1d125b73","tid":461072,"uid":155995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"樓主你幽默感美斯？"},{"pid":"320626ae30502419d9b5eb048f83eb33052ff703","tid":461072,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6e647c03120afaaab66a982ed7f113c1769854","tid":461072,"uid":53023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你幽默感美斯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個大陸人係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41870fc7dc500ea9caff550f217f10fa35be9c60","tid":461072,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"樓主你個腦美斯？"},{"pid":"9edf6b3488d8083e95bc14a059be4511a8094977","tid":461072,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計我話 美斯就得一個, 幾時輪到我"},{"pid":"8a1118292ee8c3b9e8f8e975b91986c16d1b9b2c","tid":461072,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:50:11.000Z","msg":"其實佢係想講沒事"},{"pid":"b66d98f2398523c0e135d3fb83be4770c502ba35","tid":461072,"uid":22869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gifyu.com/images/1FBB768C-6BC0-4B7D-A8D7-37151B28C8AD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgifyu.com%2Fimages%2F1FBB768C-6BC0-4B7D-A8D7-37151B28C8AD.gif&h=5402c64c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a36caad03d3180a53e9f6f27b5ce525e1eb1ca3a","tid":461072,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係熱狗"},{"pid":"7893e7ed9286bcb80661e290f73f65a29328ebbd","tid":461072,"uid":127795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299986b2285abb9bcb6ffbcb05f1dcb7b75ff8f2","tid":461072,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"其實on9又稱唔上 好笑更加唔使講<br />\n而係好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72e7acc540cb63315c0e5fdfc45fff30f8e072b","tid":461072,"uid":144982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"咁嘅垃圾po都上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cl